column5: This is the only time I'll be up at Lew O clock, since I haven't slept yet!  So.... good morning!  Gotta love newborns, have to admit, she is a cutie, wish I had a digital camera to show y'all.  Oh well, sick day tomorrow, whoops, I mean today, and if I'm lucky, some fishing this afternoon!  Have a great day.  Man, am I tired.
Lew O'clock has come and gone. Congrats on the new Daughter. Post some picks when you can.
Mornin Hooked  Newborns can be a challenge in the middle of the night, but it's all worth it in the long run
Morning! Geez, I can't even believe I'm up at this time.. must be because of waking up three days in a row at the G2G at this time trying to get a early head start...

Hahahaha, dang, I missed it!  Don't know how you guys get up this early....on purpose.  Thanks.   yeah, its like I forgot, or purged it out of my memory from my first one, he's older now and he was well worth it 10000+fold already, and she will be too!  Can't believe it, just cracked open a beer to celebrate the hand-off to the wife, whew hooo!!!  I'm free, now I sleep, wake up, and fish.....yeah right.  But ya never know.
Crap, missed Lew O'clock - not that I really wanted to see it (ha ha).   Up a little early today and heading to the grind-stone.  Only 7 more months to Lakair  (sigh)
